organic.title: Rheumatology Clinic at UWMC-Roosevelt, Seattle
organic.snippet: Rheumatology Clinic at UWMC-Roosevelt in Seattle specializes in treating complex rhematologic diseases, especially lupus—we have a lupus clinic.
